description: Thousands marched in the capital Baku and some attacked the parliament after clashes with Armenia.
title: Azerbaijan protesters demand war after Armenia clashes
title_page: Azerbaijan protesters demand war after Armenia clashes - BBC News
maintext: Officials condemned the protesters' actions. On Wednesday, the interior ministry said seven people had been arrested for "mass riots" and "resistance or use of force against a government official", and a full investigation is under way. Seven officers were injured, a statement said.
